title: Magic Knives
description: A strange creature confronts you in the dark of the night and starts flinging spell orbs your way.  Defend yourself with your magical knives and potions as long as you can. How long can you last?
Drop tiddies and merge them to create bigger tiddies. Try to reach the golden tiddies, and increase your points multiplier.

title: Super fun Yatzy
description: Very basic yatzy to play by yourself, get those dice rolling!
